name: FRigUnit_SphereTraceByObjectTypes
doc:
Sweeps a sphere against the world and return the first blocking hit. The trace is filtered by object types only, the collision response settings are ignored.
You can create custom object types in Project Setting - Collision

Start: Start of the trace in rig / global space
End: End of the trace in rig / global space
ObjectTypes: The types of objects that this trace can hit
Radius: Radius of the sphere to use for sweeping / tracing
bHit: Returns true if there was a hit
HitLocation: Hit location in rig / global Space
HitNormal: Hit normal in rig / global Space
